{
  "stem": "15610.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then come news that it's very hard life in there with a little baby.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That is too risky to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So then we didn't go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then when the kids been bigger, then we'd immigrate to Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '65, 1965.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean when I was married?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My husband, he wasn't very religious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I have problems after war to believe in-- in some-- in God or believe something, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very hard for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then I realized that be like a wild animal and not believe in nothing is worse than believe.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- I started to be a believer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I started to go to synagogue to pray, and still I am in Temple Emanuel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Belong to Temple Emanuel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I felt that I-- I-- I was in dilemma.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First I say, cannot be God if he could do this to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then [INAUDIBLE] God was also not good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- so I stay with my religion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was born Jewish, and I-- I still Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I practice.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You saw me took the candle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will be arrive in Israel?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, very hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very hard because come from communist country, you need some money to start.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And didn't let us take any money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We find work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have-- there's, in Be'er Sheva.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put us in Be'er Sheva.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I find out that somebody from [NON-ENGLISH], from Poland, is there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he has a-- a hotel and coffeehouse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he give me work to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was hard for me, but-- but I have a job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then my husband find a job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the kids went to kibbutz, all three.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- so we start.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But was not easy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
